          </div>
          <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-5 col-sm-pull-7 col-md-4 col-md-pull-8">
            <div id="basicsModal9-content2">
            </div>
            <script>
              document.getElementById('basicsModal9-content2').innerHTML =
                marked('<hr />*Several eastern philosophies, such as Yoga, Daoism, Zen, and industrial derivatives like Kaizen, promote such a world-view. Definitions of beauty, derived from these philosophies, such as Sundara or Wabi-Sabi differ from the western concepts of beauty.*');
            </script>
