            </div>
            <script>
              document.getElementById('basicsModal9-content12').innerHTML =
                marked('<hr />*We can sometimes experience these methods clash directly in inter-disciplinary software development teams where the user experience is driven by those who place experience before analysis, and the system development is led by those who place frameworks before situations (front-end vs. back-end).*');
